        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "Mari",
            "line": "*Giggle* You're working very hard, Rainbow Student.",
            "voice_idx": "3",
            "is_plus": false
        },
        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "[player]",
            "line": "Mari! What are you doing here?",
            "voice_idx": null,
            "is_plus": false
        },
        {
            "command": "character",
            "character_id": "2",
            "character_cmd": "face",
            "visual_expression": "1"
        },
        {
            "command": "character",
            "character_id": "2",
            "character_cmd": "talk"
        },
        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "Mari",
            "line": "There's only one reason I'd come to the capital city of Japan. Sightseeing!",
            "voice_idx": "4",
            "is_plus": false
        },
        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "[player]",
            "line": "S-Say whaaaat?! No way.",
            "voice_idx": null,
            "is_plus": false
        },
        {
            "command": "character",
            "character_id": "2",
            "character_cmd": "face",
            "visual_expression": "2"
        },
        {
            "command": "character",
            "character_id": "2",
            "character_cmd": "talk"
        },
        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "Mari",
            "line": "Skepticism isn't very cute, my dear.",
            "voice_idx": "5",
            "is_plus": false
        },
        {
            "command": "character",
            "character_id": "2",
            "character_cmd": "hide"
        },
        {
            "command": "background",
            "background_id": "2",
            "background_cmd": "hide"
        },
        {
            "command": "character",
            "character_id": "1",
            "character_cmd": "show"
        },
        {
            "command": "wait",
            "duration": 0.5
        },
        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "[player]",
            "line": "After what happened last time, I'd be crazy not to be skeptical. Have you come to look around the school again, Chairwoman Ohara?",
            "voice_idx": null,
            "is_plus": false
        },
        {
            "command": "character",
            "character_id": "1",
            "character_cmd": "face",
            "visual_expression": "1"
        },
        {
            "command": "character",
            "character_id": "1",
            "character_cmd": "jump"
        },
        {
            "command": "wait",
            "duration": 0.3
        },
        {
            "command": "character",
            "character_id": "1",
            "character_cmd": "talk"
        },
        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "Mari",
            "line": "Well, look at you with your sharp intuition! You can relax. This time I'm not just here to look around the school. I'm also researching school idols.",
            "voice_idx": "6",
            "is_plus": false
        },
        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "[player]",
            "line": "Huh? School idols?",
            "voice_idx": null,
            "is_plus": false
        },
        {
            "command": "character",
            "character_id": "1",
            "character_cmd": "face",
            "visual_expression": "2"
        },
        {
            "command": "character",
            "character_id": "1",
            "character_cmd": "nod",
            "character_args": [
                "-10"
            ]
        },
        {
            "command": "wait",
            "duration": 0.3
        },
        {
            "command": "character",
            "character_id": "1",
            "character_cmd": "talk"
        },
        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "Mari",
            "line": "Yes! Tokyo is a battleground for school idols. In fact, various schools are planning to use school idols to recruit students and boost their image.",
            "voice_idx": "7",
            "is_plus": false
        },
        {
            "command": "character",
            "character_id": "1",
            "character_cmd": "face",
            "visual_expression": "1"
        },
        {
            "command": "character",
            "character_id": "1",
            "character_cmd": "talk"
        },
        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "Mari",
            "line": "There's a lot to consider! Benefits and drawbacks arising from having school idols, inter-school differences, organizational support for school idols...",
            "voice_idx": "8",
            "is_plus": false
        },
        {
            "command": "character",
            "character_id": "1",
            "character_cmd": "talk"
        },
        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "Mari",
            "line": "Last time I observed the schools' facilities, customs, and traditions, but this time I'm focusing my research on the school idols themselves.",
            "voice_idx": "9",
            "is_plus": false
        },
        {
            "command": "unknown_select",
            "select_args": "||Sounds like you've come here to work!|| select_1"
        },
        {
            "command": "unknown_select",
            "select_args": "||That's a very upstanding reason for your trip.|| select_2"
        },
        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "[player]",
            "line": "Wow! Sounds like you've come here to work!",
            "voice_idx": null,
            "is_plus": false
        },
        {
            "command": "character",
            "character_id": "1",
            "character_cmd": "face",
            "visual_expression": "2"
        },
        {
            "command": "character",
            "character_id": "1",
            "character_cmd": "talk"
        },
        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "Mari",
            "line": "I always get the job done when I put my mind to it. Hey, do you wanna come with me again?",
            "voice_idx": "10",
            "is_plus": false
        },
        {
            "command": "unknown_goto",
            "goto_args": "main_1"
        },
        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "[player]",
            "line": "Hmm. You have a very upstanding reason for your trip this time. Hey, hang on! That means the whole sightseeing thing was a lie, then!",
            "voice_idx": null,
            "is_plus": false
        },
        {
            "command": "character",
            "character_id": "1",
            "character_cmd": "face",
            "visual_expression": "2"
        },
        {
            "command": "character",
            "character_id": "1",
            "character_cmd": "talk"
        },
        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "Mari",
            "line": "I can sightsee while I work. Assuming, of course, I have a capable assistant like you with me!",
            "voice_idx": "11",
            "is_plus": false
        },
        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "[player]",
            "line": "Me? But I need to hand out these flyers for our live show.",
            "voice_idx": null,
            "is_plus": false
        },
        {
            "command": "unknown_goto",
            "goto_args": "main_1"
        },
        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "[player]",
            "line": "Besides, I don't think I'll be much help even if I do join you. I'll probably just end up tagging along behind you like last time.",
            "voice_idx": null,
            "is_plus": false
        },
        {
            "command": "character",
            "character_id": "1",
            "character_cmd": "face",
            "visual_expression": "1"
        },
        {
            "command": "character",
            "character_id": "1",
            "character_cmd": "talk"
        },
        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "Mari",
            "line": "That's plenty. Remember what I said before? It's awfully gloomy to wander around an unfamiliar place all by yourself. Just having you there would put my mind at ease.",
            "voice_idx": "12",
            "is_plus": false
        },
        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "[player]",
            "line": "This coming from the last person who'd ever feel gloomy.",
            "voice_idx": null,
            "is_plus": false
        },
        {
            "command": "character",
            "character_id": "1",
            "character_cmd": "talk"
        },
        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "Mari",
            "line": "Besides, it looks like you're having trouble handing out those flyers. I bet you'd have better luck handing them out in different places rather than one spot.",
            "voice_idx": "13",
            "is_plus": false
        },
        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "[player]",
            "line": "When you put it that way, I guess you have a point.",
            "voice_idx": null,
            "is_plus": false
        },
        {
            "command": "character",
            "character_id": "1",
            "character_cmd": "talk"
        },
        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "Mari",
            "line": "If you come with me, not only can you hand out flyers far and wide, but you'll get to chat with lots of other school idols as well.",
            "voice_idx": "14",
            "is_plus": false
        },
        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "[player]",
            "line": "Chat?! You're not just gonna observe them, you're gonna talk with them face to face?!",
            "voice_idx": null,
            "is_plus": false
        },
        {
            "command": "character",
            "character_id": "1",
            "character_cmd": "face",
            "visual_expression": "2"
        },
        {
            "command": "character",
            "character_id": "1",
            "character_cmd": "talk"
        },
        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "Mari",
            "line": "Of course! I've already contacted them and received permission. What do you think? Feel like coming with me?",
            "voice_idx": "15",
            "is_plus": false
        },
        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "[player]",
            "line": "Y-Yes. I'd like to join you, please!",
            "voice_idx": null,
            "is_plus": false
        },
        {
            "command": "character",
            "character_id": "1",
            "character_cmd": "face",
            "visual_expression": "1"
        },
        {
            "command": "character",
            "character_id": "1",
            "character_cmd": "talk"
        },
        {
            "command": "speak",
            "speaker": "Mari",
            "line": "Then that settles it! Let's head off to the first school!",
            "voice_idx": "16",
            "is_plus": false
        },
